@startuml CreazioneProduzione
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor White
skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor LightBlue
    BorderColor DarkBlue
}
skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor LightGreen
    BorderColor DarkGreen
}
skinparam database {
    BackgroundColor LightYellow
    BorderColor Orange
}

title Creazione Task di Produzione

actor Utente
participant "PageProcedureLavorazioni" as Page
participant "DialogAddBackgroundTask" as Dialog
participant "ServiceProcedureLavorazioni" as Service
participant "ProductionJobScheduler" as Scheduler
participant "Hangfire" as HF
database "TaskDaEseguire" as DB

Utente -> Page: 1. Compila Procedura\n(Centro, Cliente, Formato)
activate Page
Page -> Page: 2. Aggiunge Fasi via\nDataGridElencoFasiNew
Utente -> Page: 3. Click "Add Task"
Page -> Dialog: 4. Apre dialog con contesto\n(Fase, Procedura, Sigla)
activate Dialog

Utente -> Dialog: 5. Configura task SQL\n(Query, Connection, TimeTask)
Dialog -> Dialog: 6. Valida query/connection\nasync
Dialog -> Page: 7. Restituisce TaskDaEseguireDto\ncon configurazione
deactivate Dialog

Page -> Service: 8. AddProceduraLavorazioneAsync()\ncon Fasi+Tasks
activate Service
Service -> DB: 9. INSERT Procedura+\nLavorazioniFasiDataReading+\nTaskDaEseguire
Service -> Page: 10. Success response
deactivate Service

Page -> Scheduler: 11. SyncAllAsync()\nper sincronizzazione Hangfire
activate Scheduler
Scheduler -> DB: 12. Carica task abilitati\ncon Include navigazioni
Scheduler -> Scheduler: 13. BuildHangfireKey()\nprod:{id}-{proc}-{fase}
Scheduler -> HF: 14. AddOrUpdate(key, idTask, cron)
activate HF
Scheduler -> DB: 15. UPDATE IdTaskHangFire
HF -> HF: 16. Schedula recurring job\ncon cron expression
deactivate HF
deactivate Scheduler
deactivate Page

note right of HF: Job schedulato e pronto\nper esecuzione automatica

@enduml